{"tid":1609844,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"全部睇晒佢！記住喺心！識得點做！","createTime":"2019-10-01T15:38:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T07:29:16.000Z","uid":279235,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"a98aadd9352aaa2245f2be13217fadeb213b68e7","tid":1609844,"uid":279235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:38:20.000Z","msg":"1610 在荃灣大河道中混亂期間警員拔槍近距離（約一個身位）直射向示威者，其後該示威者中槍倒地。警方確認其中實彈。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cityusuedb/videos/731753943914187/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcityusuedb%2Fvideos%2F731753943914187%2F&d=JxnAwUrH%2B1qYxVTFfur%2BVh0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=0f452f44\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cityusuedb/videos/731753943914187/</a><br />\n<br />\n荃灣大河道有示威者心口中槍倒地，本台錄到警員開槍一刻。警員當時在超近距離開槍，打向示威者左胸，該示威者約一秒後向後倒地。其後，警方消息亦確認有一名示威者因中實彈而受傷。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkucampustv/videos/542398913195804/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkucampustv%2Fvideos%2F542398913195804%2F&d=JxnAwUrH%2B1qYxVTFfur%2BVh0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=969a606e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkucampustv/videos/542398913195804/</a><br />\n<br />\n1613 荃灣大河道中附近有示威者左邊胸口被槍打中，不斷高呼：「我心口好痛」，並且有大量血液從心口湧出。期間記者不斷問示威者名稱，其自稱曾志健（同音），為數月示威以來首次有示威者中實彈。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cityusuedb/videos/2355215818126101/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcityusuedb%2Fvideos%2F2355215818126101%2F&d=JxnAwUrH%2B1qYxVTFfur%2BVh0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=9934d2a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cityusuedb/videos/2355215818126101/</a><br />\n<br />\n16:29 警方剛才於海壩街向示威者發射疑似實彈，該名示威者立刻倒地，面色蒼白，胸口大片血跡。他大叫自己名字「曾志健」（同音），隨後不省人事。警方當時忙於制服另一名示威者，該名示威者叫警察盡快救治中槍傷者。<br />\n急救員為中槍傷者急救並將其送上擔架床。警方其後拉起封鎖線，不准記者接近拍攝。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkpusupresscom/videos/955608894783449/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkpusupresscom%2Fvideos%2F955608894783449%2F&d=JxnAwUrH%2B1qYxVTFfur%2BVh0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=19bd1344\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkpusupresscom/videos/955608894783449/</a><br />\n<br />\n荃灣有示威者手部中彈，急救員初步診斷為手骨爆裂。<br />\n<img src=\"https://bit.ly/2nvXmaX\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2nvXmaX&h=89e12681&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/busueb/photos/2375431862540995/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbusueb%2Fphotos%2F2375431862540995%2F&d=JxnAwUrH%2B1qYxVTFfur%2BVh0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=8e82026c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/busueb/photos/2375431862540995/</a><br />\n<br />\n有大批防暴警員突然衝向龍翔道，與示威者引起激烈衝突，期間一名警員叫另外的警員「開槍」，此時有警員掏出實彈手槍指向前方，面露興奮笑容，並配合警方防線後退。當時前方有多名包括本會在內的記者，並且傳出一下疑似實彈槍聲，未知是否已開槍。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/busueb/videos/273243563559179/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbusueb%2Fvideos%2F273243563559179%2F&d=JxnAwUrH%2B1qYxVTFfur%2BVh0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=9aa9b808\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/busueb/videos/273243563559179/</a><br />\n<br />\n鑽石山鳳德道及蒲崗村道交界，有大量人士聚集，兩段路面已設路障；亦有不少人在灑溪錢，有人舉著徐步高的遺照，指李家超誤殺好人。<br />\n<img src=\"https://bit.ly/2nhWneF\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2nhWneF&h=d54a81b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/busueb/photos/2374746585942856/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbusueb%2Fphotos%2F2374746585942856%2F&d=JxnAwUrH%2B1qYxVTFfur%2BVh0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=dcd66e72\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/busueb/photos/2374746585942856/</a>"},{"pid":"be6de5b4e8e1332cbb37862bfaf85f38a1a281ff","tid":1609844,"uid":242437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:20:09.000Z","msg":"（聽朝西九裁判院要人) 929金鐘被捕義士家人的話<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1610027\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1610027</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1d6aa333efdf073678635418cd4a581029b00204","tid":1609844,"uid":242437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:20:20.000Z","msg":"【929提堂】無事就手足, 而家幾十個手足被人告暴動呀<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1609959\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1609959</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e60847f913fe6fc19caa1fe7e2c128b8722fbf70","tid":1609844,"uid":279235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T16:49:14.000Z","msg":"聽日都爆唔起嘅，唔使再講乜兄弟手足<br />\n三登多年CD-ROM，諗住入嚟有番作為<br />\n若然冇需要我嘅地方，做返CD-ROM算"},{"pid":"aeb01c7a112445209de7d22b94da3d799e46110a","tid":1609844,"uid":52228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:00:07.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"02ae9f3d4d351b9f6281d1456e6ecc55e37a8a69","tid":1609844,"uid":196020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:03:00.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ac1b7bb1aa00e0e40669c77c53b410d68a8e92ec","tid":1609844,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T17:22:42.000Z","msg":"只有罷工罷市才能夠救大家<br />\n請全民無&middot;限&middot;期罷工罷課，救自己、救義士！迫政府讓步！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1610341\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1610341</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">今日政府宣布，香港各區發生暴動！</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">亦即係話，今日只要出過街嘅非警察人士，都有機會告你參與暴動</span>！<span style=\"color: red;\">要去狗屋坐48個鐘，而且定罪嘅話一坐就幾年</span>！<br />\n<br />\n打工反學嘅你，為你自己將來，呼籲大家，<span style=\"color: red;\">盡快組織無限期罷工、罷課</span>！<span style=\"color: gold;\">只有咁，先可以癱瘓社會運作，直到政府宣布徹底妥協，答應五大訴求為止！</span>"},{"pid":"a56c9f98e6044d512f8e4ed140bd2422f3e337e4","tid":1609844,"uid":112748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T18:29:14.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"8dbef8ba58c011782ad6270b30cc1089d06e0cb9","tid":1609844,"uid":